<p>A Italy virtual private server (VPS) is a server designed and run as a replica of a dedicated server. In other words, a VPS is similar to a dedicated server, yet cheaper than dedicated hosting. A virtual private server hosting is ideal for businesses that have significant traffic or need to have an edge over other companies in a certain geographical location. For instance, if you are based in the United States, but you want to remain in Australia and have a business operation in Japan, then VPS would be a good option.</p>
