<p>One big advantage that Italy VPS hosting has is that it reduces the cost per physical server. A VPS consists of one physical server and two or more virtual servers. Each virtual server is completely isolated and does not have any effect on the other virtual servers. Thus, the performance and functionality of each virtual server remain unaffected by other VPS that are installed on the same physical server. With this design, the overall cost of running a VPS can be reduced.</p>
